<p class="">I am not talking about what is in the Parliament Act but about good constitutional doctrine, and if the right hon. Gentleman seriously wishes to urge explicitly that another place ought to have the power to determine when a General Election shall take place and the issues upon which it shall be fought, let him say so and we shall argue it out.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
